data.description: This open concept Cherry Creek studio has been nicely updated and is entirely move-in ready!  New flooring, crisp paint and a bathroom remodel completed in 2023.  The kitchen has newer cabinetry, stainless steel appliances and butcher block countertops.  This unit has central air conditioning and a large walk-in closet.  The floor plan is spacious…enjoy having a dedicated dining area and office space while still easily accommodating a king-sized bed, dresser and two end tables.  Enjoy the beautiful pool, clubhouse and picnic area…all ideally located just a short distance from this unit.  Easily access several bike trails and parks including the Cherry Creek Trail, Potenza Park, Garfield Park, Infinity Park and Lollipop Lake.  Enjoy the convenience of living near many big box retailers and grocery stores including Target, World Market, Home Depot, Whole Foods and your choice of two King Soopers.  Meet friends for brunch at Bull and Bush or at Esthers.  Grab a quick lunch at City Set (Panera, Garbanzo, Native Foods and Café Rio).  Eat at Jax, Osaka Sushi, Mod Market or Las Delicias for Dinner…the options are endless in this accessible location.  Furniture items also for sale if interested on a separate bill of sale.
